text: Anwar ul Haq Kakar (, ) is a Pakistani politician. He was the Caretaker Prime Minister of Pakistan from 14 August 2023 until 4 March 2024. Before that, he was the spokesperson of the Government of Balochistan from 2015 to 2017. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Balochistan (Pakistan) Category:Independent politicians Category:Date of birth missing (living people)
